{"tid":1219326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】教育局長致函全港校長校監　促按條例處理罷教教師","createTime":"2019-06-13T19:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T01:40:49.000Z","uid":80516,"like":10,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5edffb650cfa2132a062d65fdc187ac0817b75","tid":1219326,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:22:10.000Z","msg":"撰文：袁澍<br />\n2019-06-13 23:18<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-06-13 23:18<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議繼續升溫，近日更相繼有學生聯署發起罷課行動。昨日（12日）金鐘立法會一帶示威者與警方發生衝突後，教協宣布全港罷課，教育局局長楊潤雄今日（13日）傍晚致函全港學校的校長及校監，題為《緊守崗位 守護學生》，表明教育局堅決反對教育團體罷課及罷教；同時若有教師未經批准而缺席，學校應按照相關資助條例、僱傭條例及校本政策處理。<br />\n<br />\n教育局正在和學校緊密聯絡，並了解學生缺席和教師人手調配的情況，稱以便提供適切支援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2908465/org/1c510b0788f74405d55fa796630d41b5.jpg/TH9uUscG5tnMcVQalqYT1tqVKVDcLklkwSCu8OsgrvA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2908465%2Forg%2F1c510b0788f74405d55fa796630d41b5.jpg%2FTH9uUscG5tnMcVQalqYT1tqVKVDcLklkwSCu8OsgrvA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=63a53453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在昨日爆發警民衝突後，教協宣佈推動全港罷課罷教行動。（資料圖片/余俊亮攝）<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>年輕人參與暴動 受傷令人心痛</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄在信函中表示，昨日灣仔及中西區一帶有人佔據和堵塞道路，甚至暴動，當中有不少年輕人參與，有人受傷流血，令人心痛。他並指有人在社交媒體號召群眾破壞社會秩序，是煽動情緒，製造恐慌，校方應守護學生，告誡同學不要參與違法行為，以安全為重，勿前往有可能有危險的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2911799/org/9e8606e5cd31f621281b7295aa655702.jpg/55iFYjODguhtCmiGrTN_vdVl9IEywg9MuiCCTLoggkw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2911799%2Forg%2F9e8606e5cd31f621281b7295aa655702.jpg%2F55iFYjODguhtCmiGrTN_vdVl9IEywg9MuiCCTLoggkw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1ec4c5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄批評有人煽動學生參與違法行動。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n函件附政府修訂《逃犯條例》小冊子<br />\n<br />\n針對最近有教育團體發動罷課及罷教活動，教育局堅決反對，並指學校是學生學習的地方，任何人都不應以學校作為表達政治訴求的場地。<br />\n<br />\n函件續指，教師在任何情況下均須履行職責，緊守工作崗位，行為亦需要符合專業操守。教育局稱，學校作為僱主，有責任管理員工及監察他們的工作表現；若個別教師在工作時間未經學校批准而缺席，或沒有履行職務，學校須明確指出有關行為實屬不當，並應當按相關資助則例、僱傭條例及校本政策處理。<br />\n<br />\n信函中並附有保安局關於政府修訂《逃犯條例》的小冊子，但又指香港是一個多元社會，尊重不同意見，但老師應該引導學生多角度思考，以和平、合法方式表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2908434/org/6c945577f34663b03cec47fbb41506cd.jpg/U3Kfzjkx3EPyk9cypR-DJ_NGXfZxNG4IU3iZYVN4mWE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2908434%2Forg%2F6c945577f34663b03cec47fbb41506cd.jpg%2FU3Kfzjkx3EPyk9cypR-DJ_NGXfZxNG4IU3iZYVN4mWE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=63ab459f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2908432/org/c30b107c29dd4352fb29f18b4efcdda7.jpg/WQubRcplox0dDhp4sXRWcUZFHpJWeh8SIRs1SyEbNUs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2908432%2Forg%2Fc30b107c29dd4352fb29f18b4efcdda7.jpg%2FWQubRcplox0dDhp4sXRWcUZFHpJWeh8SIRs1SyEbNUs&h=627782f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2908431/org/cbe14c0b08e62c87e8197b88c97f8d9a.jpg/nVHT1Gbrxuu1fl9ggdMmLJIMEsF-On7czfFr6s3xa-o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2908431%2Forg%2Fcbe14c0b08e62c87e8197b88c97f8d9a.jpg%2FnVHT1Gbrxuu1fl9ggdMmLJIMEsF-On7czfFr6s3xa-o&h=d0f4c7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏愨道與添華道交界有逾40市民聚集搬運大量物資，期間有超過50警察到場查問，立法會議員譚文豪、梁耀忠、尹兆堅、張超雄到場協助，警方最終撤退。（張浩維攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2908244/org/d9f14764b5962a62867dfe906f3f83b6.jpg/1426Ml7eZA8S2VLDLZDhCqnJErwshS24V7fcJn233CY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2908244%2Forg%2Fd9f14764b5962a62867dfe906f3f83b6.jpg%2F1426Ml7eZA8S2VLDLZDhCqnJErwshS24V7fcJn233CY&h=680bbf51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威者於昨日前往立法會、政總一帶抗議。下午三時後示威者開始衝破防線，向立法會推進，期間警方發射催淚彈、布袋彈及催淚水劑。（張浩維攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2908090/org/ee07dc2e27583c66b82de99d76f698a3.jpg/8PV_pNo6afGp7ZPYVBERK_G81IfUmOncicsjNonLIzY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2908090%2Forg%2Fee07dc2e27583c66b82de99d76f698a3.jpg%2F8PV_pNo6afGp7ZPYVBERK_G81IfUmOncicsjNonLIzY&h=1f81fe08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n添馬公園一帶有大量年輕人來「野餐」。 現場沒有任何警察駐守。（張浩維攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2907410/org/8e17b87e77de380e5a77550e6342a987.jpg/mJkvBllOne1rZyx9IMSO2wXt_sdeVxKDygH1wsoB9cI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2907410%2Forg%2F8e17b87e77de380e5a77550e6342a987.jpg%2FmJkvBllOne1rZyx9IMSO2wXt_sdeVxKDygH1wsoB9cI&h=0295d4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者之後退到海富中心位置，警方將催淚彈擲上海富天橋。（張浩維攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340141/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%A0%A1%E7%9B%A3-%E4%BF%83%E6%8C%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%BD%B7%E6%95%99%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB?fbclid=IwAR3BsIv0J4w3w0HuKQQJRHFh6W1D3e4v9oAyVpwUXFv6BkXllx203TCQ3dk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F340141%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2587%25BD%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%259B%25A3-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3BsIv0J4w3w0HuKQQJRHFh6W1D3e4v9oAyVpwUXFv6BkXllx203TCQ3dk&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADSiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=501fb412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340141/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%A0%A1%E7%9B%A3-%E4%BF%83%E6%8C%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%BD%B7%E6%95%99%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB?fbclid=IwAR3BsIv0J4w3w0HuKQQJRHFh6W1D3e4v9oAyVpwUXFv6BkXllx203TCQ3dk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3bf301a67f889d701e349292c8ee41e7f1cd331a","tid":1219326,"uid":2718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"607550eb80d2a6552d211ab2f785b19e7e290f44","tid":1219326,"uid":2718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:24:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"736e2cb9b2be791c727258f6793cd8865a1aeba4","tid":1219326,"uid":2718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:25:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b048e28ddffb1c35875091caa854339f217b1f5","tid":1219326,"uid":96411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:26:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5dc53734aab7b2b331c7e8425d4fc14c28edd3fa","tid":1219326,"uid":250994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:26:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bc3a005925a4801f4d6414dc5e4d14fa50dd0b5","tid":1219326,"uid":2718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:26:35.000Z","msg":"推啊！！"},{"pid":"d48127b70e8ec1087ec56aaf5db0c99cd332c67c","tid":1219326,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f130f9184d247b904309578b115d0e6f8787eac7","tid":1219326,"uid":50835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13